d_pict_pagan = {
	color={ 122 165 70 }
	color2={ 220 220 0 }
	
	capital = 252
	
	title = "ARCH_DRUID"
	title_female = "ARCH_DRUIDESS"
	foa = "ARCH_DRUID_FOA"
	
	short_name = yes
	
	# Always exists
	landless = yes

	allow = {
		religion = pict_pagan_reformed
		num_of_holy_sites = 3
		piety = 500
		has_religion_feature = religion_temporal_head
	}
	
	# Controls a religion
	controls_religion = pict_pagan_reformed
	
	religion = pict_pagan_reformed
	
	# Cannot be held as a secondary title
	primary = no
	
	dynasty_title_names = no 	# Will not be named "Seljuk", etc.
}

			culture_group = celtic
			NOT = {
				OR = {
					trait = northaugustus
					top_liege = { trait = northaugustus }
				}
			}
			NOT = { has_landed_title = k_gwynedd }
			OR = {
				custom_tooltip = {
					text = henis_wyren_tooltip
					has_global_flag = henis_wyren_created
				}
				AND = {
					lower_tier_than = KING
					primary_title = {
						OR = {
							title = d_osmaeliog
							title = d_arfon
						}
					}
					completely_controls = d_osmaeliog
					completely_controls = c_arfon
					independent = yes
					prestige = 1000
					age = 20
				}
			}
		}

e_gaul = {		# Imperium Galliarum
	color={ 180 70 130 }
	color2={ 255 255 255 }
	
	capital = 903 # Arelate

	culture = romanogallic
	short_name = yes
	assimilate = no
	
	hebrew = "Tzar'fat"
	french = "Gaulle"
	occitan = "Gaulle"
	arpitan = "Gaulle"
	
	creation_requires_capital = no
	
	title = "IMPERATOR"
	title_female = "IMPERATRIX"
	purple_born_heirs = yes
	dynasty_title_names = no
	
	dignity = 1000
	
	allow = {
		OR = {
			culture_group = imperiale
			culture = romanobritish
		}
		age = 20
		title_gender_requirement_trigger = yes
		realm_size = 350
		prestige = 2000
		NOT = { trait = incapable }
		tier = KING
		NOT = { trait = slow }
		NOT = { trait = dwarf }
		NOT = { trait = leper }
		NOT = { trait = blinded }
		NOT = { trait = imbecile }
		NOT = { trait = eunuch }
		NOT = { trait = incapable }
		custom_tooltip = {
			text = senate_restored_tooltip
			hidden_tooltip = { any_demesne_title = { has_title_flag = senate_restored_title } }
		}
		conditional_tooltip = {
			trigger = {
				e_visigoths = { has_holder = yes }
			}
			e_visigoths = { has_holder = no }
		}
	}

	# SUB-ROMAN KINGDOMS IN GAUL
	
	k_broceliande = {
		color={ 86 191 151 }
		color2={ 255 255 255 }
		
		culture = armorican

		allow = {
			culture_group = celtic
			NOT = {
				OR = {
					trait = northaugustus
					top_liege = { trait = northaugustus }
				}
			}
			OR = {
				custom_tooltip = {
					text = broceliande_tooltip
					NOT = { has_global_flag = broceliande_renamed }
				}
				AND = {
					completely_controls = c_vannes
					completely_controls = c_quimper
					completely_controls = c_broceliande
					completely_controls = c_rennes
				}
			}
		}
		
		title_prefix = "BRITISH_KINGDOM_OF"
		
		capital = 205 # Darioritum/Vannes
		assimilate = no		
	}
	k_benoic = {
		color={ 165 165 165 }
		color2={ 255 255 255 }
		
		culture = armorican

		allow = {
			culture_group = celtic
			NOT = {
				OR = {
					trait = northaugustus
					top_liege = { trait = northaugustus }
				}
			}
			conditional_tooltip = {
				trigger = {
					OR = { 
						has_global_flag = benoic_renamed
						has_global_flag = benoic_destroyed
					}
					NOT = { has_global_flag = benoic_armorica_created }
				}
				AND = {
					completely_controls = c_ynys_trebes
					completely_controls = c_constantia
					completely_controls = c_rennes
				}
			}
			conditional_tooltip = {
				trigger = {
					has_global_flag = benoic_destroyed
					NOT = { has_global_flag = benoic_armorica_created }
				}
				culture = armorican
			}
		}
		
		title_prefix = "BRITISH_KINGDOM_OF"
		
		capital = 78 # Ynys Trebes
		assimilate = no
		
	}

	}
	
	k_gaul = {
		color={ 145 110 85 }
		color2={ 255 255 255 }
		
		culture = romanogallic
		
		capital = 185	# Soissons
		assimilate = no
		dignity = 6

		title = "DUX"
		title_prefix = "DOMAIN_OF"
		
		allow = {
			is_roman_culture_trigger = yes
			NOT = { has_global_flag = roman_provinces_gaul_restored }
			NOT = { tier = EMPEROR }
			OR = {
				completely_controls = c_reims
				completely_controls = c_tours
				completely_controls = c_agedincum
				completely_controls = c_rotomagus
				completely_controls = c_treverorum

	franconian = "Frankeríhhi"

	arpitan = "France"
	hebrew = "Tzar'fat"

	# title = "FRANKLANDKING"
	# title_female = "FRANKLANDKING_female"
	title = "KAISER"
	title_female = "KAISER_female"
	
	allow = {
		are_dejure_changes_allowed_trigger = yes
		is_frankish_culture_trigger = yes
		OR = {
			has_religion_feature = religion_no_leader
			AND = {
				custom_tooltip = {
					text = has_religious_head
					religion_head = {
						always = yes
					}
				}
				religion_head = {
					OR = {
						top_liege = { character = ROOT }
						opinion = {
							who = ROOT
							value = 60
						}
					}
				}
			}
		}
		title_gender_requirement_trigger = yes
		age = 25
		prisoner = no
		independent = yes
		prestige = 3000
		OR = {
			piety = 750
			has_character_modifier = true_christian_knight
			AND = {
				trait = zealous
				trait = diligent
				trait = ambitious
			}
		}
		NOT = { trait = incapable }
		NOT = { trait = imbecile }
		completely_controls_region = custom_roman_soissons_area
		completely_controls_region = custom_frankish_area
		realm_size = 450
		e_western_roman_empire = { has_holder = no }
	}
	
	gain_effect = {
		prestige = 500
		piety = 100
		change_diplomacy = 1
	}
}

						culture = oldsaxon
						culture = saxon

					independent = yes
					prestige = 1500
					num_of_count_titles_in_realm = 15
				}
				AND = {
					is_frankish_culture_trigger = yes
					custom_tooltip = {
						text = saxony_subjugated_tooltip
						has_global_flag = saxony_subjugated
					}
				}
				AND = {
					culture_group = germanic
					top_liege = { 
						culture_group = germanic
						tier = EMPEROR
					}
				}
			}	
			conditional_tooltip = {
				trigger = {
					is_roman_emperor_trigger = yes
				}
				is_roman_emperor_trigger = no
			}
		}

	k_thuringia = {
		color={ 47 109 157 }
		color2={ 255 255 255 }
		
		capital = 1192  # Erfurt
		
		title_prefix = "GAUL_KINGDOM_OF"
		
		culture = oldthuringian
		assimilate = no
		#creation_requires_capital = no
		
		allow = {
			OR = {
				AND = {
					age = 20
					OR = {
						culture = oldthuringian
						culture = thuringian
					}
					independent = yes
					prestige = 1500
					num_of_count_titles_in_realm = 20
				}
				AND = {
					is_frankish_culture_trigger = yes
					custom_tooltip = {
						text = thuringia_subjugated_tooltip
						has_global_flag = thuringia_subjugated
					}
				}
				AND = {
					culture_group = germanic
					top_liege = { 
						culture_group = germanic
						tier = EMPEROR
					}
				}
			}
			conditional_tooltip = {
				trigger = {
					is_roman_emperor_trigger = yes
				}
				is_roman_emperor_trigger = no
			}
			hidden_tooltip = {
				OR = {
					ai = no
					is_frankish_culture_trigger = no
					year = 700
				}
			}
		}

	k_frisia = {
		color={ 186 167 68 }
		color2={ 255 255 255 }
		
		capital = 166	# Utrecht/Traiectum
		
		# title_prefix = "GAUL_KINGDOM_OF"
		
		culture = oldfrisian
		assimilate = no
		
		allow = {
			OR = {
				AND = {
					age = 20
					OR = {
						is_ingvaeonic_culture_trigger = yes
						AND = {
							is_north_germanic_trigger = yes
							lower_tier_than = KING
							capital_scope = { region = custom_frisia }
						}
					}
					independent = yes
					prestige = 1500
					num_of_count_titles_in_realm = 15
				}
				AND = {
					is_frankish_culture_trigger = yes
					custom_tooltip = {
						text = frisia_subjugated_tooltip
						has_global_flag = frisia_subjugated
					}
				}
				AND = {
					culture_group = germanic
					top_liege = { 
						culture_group = germanic
						tier = EMPEROR
					}
				}
			}	
			conditional_tooltip = {
				trigger = {
					is_roman_emperor_trigger = yes
				}
				is_roman_emperor_trigger = no
			}
		}

	k_alemannia = {
		color={ 176 173 173 }
		color2={ 255 255 255 }
		
		capital = 1096	# Albuinsbaar
		
		title_prefix = "GAUL_KINGDOM_OF"
		
		culture = oldalemannic
		assimilate = no
		#creation_requires_capital = no
		
		allow = {
			OR = {
				AND = {
					age = 20
					OR = {
						culture = oldalemannic
						culture = alemannic
					}
					independent = yes
					prestige = 1500
					num_of_count_titles_in_realm = 15
				}
				AND = {
					is_frankish_culture_trigger = yes
					custom_tooltip = {
						text = alemannia_subjugated_tooltip
						has_global_flag = alemannia_subjugated
					}
				}
				AND = {
					culture_group = germanic
					top_liege = { 
						culture_group = germanic
						tier = EMPEROR
					}
				}
			}	
			conditional_tooltip = {
				trigger = {
					is_roman_emperor_trigger = yes
				}
				is_roman_emperor_trigger = no
			}
			hidden_tooltip = {
				OR = {
					ai = no
					is_frankish_culture_trigger = no
					year = 700
				}
			}
		}

	k_franconia = {
		color = { 150 140 90 }
		color2={ 255 255 255 }
		
		capital = 1072		# Untarrheingau
		
		culture = oldfrankish
		
		assimilate = no
		
		allow = {
			has_global_flag = franconia_created
			OR = {
				is_frankish_culture_trigger = yes
				AND = {
					culture_group = germanic
					top_liege = { 
						culture_group = germanic
						tier = EMPEROR
					}
				}
			}
			conditional_tooltip = {
				trigger = {
					is_roman_emperor_trigger = yes
				}
				is_roman_emperor_trigger = no
			}
		}
	}

# ROMAN TITLES IN BRITAIN

e_roman_britannia = {
	color={ 210 90 45 }
	color2={ 255 255 255 }
	
	culture = roman
	
	capital = 47 # Londinium
	short_name = yes
	assimilate = no
	
	french = "Britaigne"
#	norman = "Britaine"
	occitan = "Bretanha"
	arpitan = "Bretagne"
	hebrew = "Bretanyah"
	
	creation_requires_capital = no
	
	title = "IMPERATOR"
	title_female = "IMPERATRIX"
	purple_born_heirs = yes
	dynasty_title_names = no
	
	dignity = 1000
	
	allow = {
		is_roman_culture_trigger = yes
		age = 20
		title_gender_requirement_trigger = yes
		realm_size = 150
		NOT = { trait = incapable }
		custom_tooltip = {  
			text = senate_restored_tooltip
			hidden_tooltip = { any_demesne_title = { has_title_flag = senate_restored_title } }
		}
		tier = KING
		OR = {
			has_landed_title = k_maxima_cesariensis
			has_landed_title = k_flavia_cesariensis
			has_landed_title = k_britannia_prima
			has_landed_title = k_britannia_secunda
			has_landed_title = k_valentia
		}
		NOT = { trait = slow }
		NOT = { trait = dwarf }
		NOT = { trait = leper }
		NOT = { trait = blinded }
		NOT = { trait = imbecile }
		NOT = { trait = eunuch }
		NOT = { trait = incapable }
	}

	k_britannia_prima = {
		# color={ 110 150 205 }
		# color = { 80 180 220 }
		color = { 225 125 85 }
		color2={ 255 255 255 }
		
		culture = roman
		
		capital = 11 # Corinium
		dignity = 8
		
		assimilate = no
		
		title = "GOVERNOR"
		title_female = "DOMINA"
		title_prefix = "PROVINCE_OF"
		purple_born_heirs = yes
		
		allow = {
			completely_controls = c_corinium
			OR = {
				trait = northaugustus
				culture_group = imperiale
				AND = {
					top_liege = { trait = northaugustus }
					culture = romanobritish
				}
			}
			briton_king_roman_province_creation_block_trigger = yes
			custom_tooltip = {
				text = calc_true_if_5_tooltip
				calc_true_if = {
					amount = 5
					completely_controls = c_glevum
					completely_controls = c_burrium
					completely_controls = c_isca_siluria
					completely_controls = c_moridunum
					completely_controls = c_viroconium	
					completely_controls = c_arfon
					completely_controls = c_calleva
					completely_controls = c_venta
					completely_controls = c_durnovaria
					completely_controls = c_isca_dumnonia
				}
			}
			tooltip = {
				calc_true_if = {
					amount = 5
					completely_controls = c_glevum
					completely_controls = c_burrium
					completely_controls = c_isca_siluria
					completely_controls = c_moridunum
					completely_controls = c_viroconium	
					completely_controls = c_arfon
					completely_controls = c_calleva
					completely_controls = c_venta
					completely_controls = c_durnovaria
					completely_controls = c_isca_dumnonia
				}
			}
		}
		
		gain_effect = {
			change_diplomacy = 1
			hidden_tooltip = {
				k_britannia_prima = {
					gender_succ = agnatic
				}
			}
		}
	}

	gain_effect = {
		change_diplomacy = 1
		change_martial = 1
		hidden_tooltip = {
			if = {
				limit = {
					primary_title = { NOT = { has_law = ze_administration_laws_2 } }
				}
				primary_title = {
					add_law = { 
						law = ze_administration_laws_2 
						cooldown = no 
						opinion_effect = no 
					}
				}
			}
			e_roman_britannia = {
				add_law = { 
					law = succ_byzantine_elective
					cooldown = no 
					opinion_effect = no
				}
			}
		}
		if = {
			limit = { has_character_modifier = maxima_caesariensis_decaying_realm }
			remove_character_modifier = maxima_caesariensis_decaying_realm
		}
	}
}

		}

		age = 20
		prestige = 1500
		realm_size = 60
		diplomacy = 15
		martial = 12

			trait = slow
			trait = dwarf
			trait = leper
			trait = blinded
			trait = imbecile
			trait = eunuch

		completely_controls = c_rennes
		completely_controls = c_nantes
		completely_controls = c_ynys_trebes

		completely_controls = c_augustodurum

				culture_group = celtic

					OR = {

				OR = {
					custom_tooltip = {

					}
					AND = {
						has_landed_title = k_broceliande
						completely_controls = c_ratiatum
						completely_controls = c_vetraria
					}
				}
			}
		}

					}

						primary_title = { title = d_ui_neill }
						primary_title = { title = d_ulaid }
					}
					completely_controls = c_letterkenny
					completely_controls = c_ailech
					completely_controls = c_doire
					completely_controls = c_ui_tuirtri
					completely_controls = c_clogher

					prestige = 1000
				}
				custom_tooltip = {
					text = northern_ui_neill_tooltip

				}
			}
			culture_group = celtic
			NOT = {
				OR = {
					trait = northaugustus

				}
			}
		}

e_scandinavia = {
	color={ 80 160 200 }
	color2={ 255 255 0 }
	
	culture = dane
	
	dynasty_title_names = no
	assimilate = no
	
	capital = 845 # Vasksala/Uppsala

	gain_effect = {
		change_diplomacy = 1
		change_martial = 1
	}
	
	allow = {
		has_global_flag = scandinavia_created
		is_north_germanic_trigger = yes
		age = 25
		prestige = 1500
		num_of_count_titles_in_realm = 100
		realm_martial = 25
		realm_diplomacy = 25
		realm_stewardship = 25
		NOT = { trait = incapable }
	}
}

# PAPAL LEGATE in BRITANNIA

	k_nuncio_britanniae = {
		color={ 200 200 165 }
		color2={ 255 255 255 }
		
		title = "NUNCIO"
		foa = "NUNCIO_FOA"
		
		short_name = yes
		
		dignity = 100 
		
		capital = 111 	# Armagh
		
		creation_requires_capital = no
		
		# Always exists
		landless = yes
		
		# Controls a religion
		controls_religion = catholic
		
		religion = catholic
		culture = roman
		
		# Cannot be held as a secondary title
		primary = yes
		
		dynasty_title_names = no
		location_ruler_title = yes
		
		# Regnal names
		male_names = {
			Gregorius Benedictus Leo Bonifacius Adrianus
			Celestinus Martinus Honorius Callixtus Pelagius Adeodatus
			Agapetus Gelasius Anicetus
			Simplicius Silverius Vigilius Severinus Constantine Romanus
			Aemilius Albanus Ambrosinus Antoninus Attilius Aulus Aurelius
			Cassianus Cassius Cato Cornelius Domitianus Fabianus Germanus
			Horatius Iulianus Longinus Marianus Maximianus Maximus Octavianus
			Regulus Romolus Rufus
			Secundus Septimus Severus Sextus Tacitus Valerianus Vespasianus
		}
	}

		d_cohors_cornoviorum = {
			color={ 110 110 160 }
			color2={ 255 255 255 }
			
			capital = 41 # Old Tyne
			
			name_tier = count
			
			# Hire Trigger
			allow = {
				conditional_tooltip = {
					trigger = {
						NOT = {
							is_alternate_start = yes
						}
					}
					OR = {
						is_hellenic_group_religion_trigger = yes
						religion_group = pagan_group
						religion_group = christian
					}
					NOT = {
						culture = pictish
						culture = oldirish
						is_ingvaeonic_culture_trigger = yes
					}
				}
			}
			
			religion = roman_pagan
			culture = romanobritish
			
			dynasty_title_names = no
			mercenary = yes
			used_for_dynasty_names = no
			
			title = "LEGATUS"
			foa = "legatus_foa"

			landless = yes
			primary = yes
			# independent = yes

			mercenary_type = d_cohors_cornoviorum_composition
		}

			religion = arian
			
			allow = {
				conditional_tooltip = {
					trigger = {
						NOT = {
							is_alternate_start = yes
						}
					}
					culture = burgundian
					OR = {
						has_landed_title = k_burgundy
						AND = {
							has_landed_title = e_visigoths
							e_visigoths = { has_title_flag = empire_claimed_burgundians }
						}
						top_liege = {
							OR = {
								has_landed_title = k_burgundy
								AND = {
									has_landed_title = e_visigoths
									e_visigoths = { has_title_flag = empire_claimed_burgundians }
								}
							}
						}
					}
				}
			}
			
			dynasty_title_names = no
			mercenary = yes
			used_for_dynasty_names = no

			title = "CAPTAIN"
			foa = "CAPTAIN_FOA"

			landless = yes
			primary = yes

			mercenary_type = d_burgundian_guard_composition

			strength_growth_per_century = 0.3
		}
